{
  "video_id": "b2Jv8vC-m3g",
  "title": "The key to a better malaria vaccine | Faith Osier",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13754.0,
      "end_time": 18420.0,
      "text": "There are 200 million clinical cases"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18444.0,
      "end_time": 22846.0,
      "text": "of falciparum malaria in Africa every year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22871.0,
      "end_time": 25790.0,
      "text": "resulting in half a million deaths."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 26395.0,
      "end_time": 30204.0,
      "text": "I would like to talk to you about malaria vaccines."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 30807.0,
      "end_time": 36405.0,
      "text": "The ones that we have made to date are simply not good enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 36998.0,
      "end_time": 38147.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 38474.0,
      "end_time": 42458.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve been working at it for 100 plus years."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 42950.0,
      "end_time": 46556.0,
      "text": "When we started, technology was limited."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 46966.0,
      "end_time": 53847.0,
      "text": "We could see just a tiny fraction of what the parasite really looked like."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 54466.0,
      "end_time": 57831.0,
      "text": "Today, we are awash with technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 57855.0,
      "end_time": 61910.0,
      "text": "advanced imaging and omics platforms --"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 61934.0,
      "end_time": 66143.0,
      "text": "genomics, transcriptomics, proteomics."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 66620.0,
      "end_time": 70493.0,
      "text": "These tools have given us a clearer view"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 70517.0,
      "end_time": 74810.0,
      "text": "of just how complex the parasite really is."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 75365.0,
      "end_time": 77991.0,
      "text": "However, in spite of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 78160.0,
      "end_time": 83516.0,
      "text": "our approach to vaccine design has remained pretty rudimentary."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 84400.0,
      "end_time": 88460.0,
      "text": "To make a good vaccine, we must go back to basics"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 88484.0,
      "end_time": 93900.0,
      "text": "to understand how our bodies handle this complexity."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 94460.0,
      "end_time": 98657.0,
      "text": "People who are frequently infected with malaria"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 98681.0,
      "end_time": 100148.0,
      "text": "learn to deal with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 100689.0,
      "end_time": 103990.0,
      "text": "They get the infection, but they don&#39;t get ill."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 104688.0,
      "end_time": 108307.0,
      "text": "The recipe is encoded in antibodies."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 108903.0,
      "end_time": 112887.0,
      "text": "My team went back to our complex parasite,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 112911.0,
      "end_time": 117839.0,
      "text": "probed it with samples from Africans who had overcome malaria"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 117863.0,
      "end_time": 119688.0,
      "text": "to answer the question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 119712.0,
      "end_time": 123759.0,
      "text": "\"What does a successful antibody response look like?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 124212.0,
      "end_time": 127514.0,
      "text": "We found over 200 proteins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 127538.0,
      "end_time": 131751.0,
      "text": "many of which are not on the radar for malaria vaccines."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 132141.0,
      "end_time": 137322.0,
      "text": "My research community may be missing out important parts of the parasite."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 138283.0,
      "end_time": 143547.0,
      "text": "Until recently, when one had identified a protein of interest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 143572.0,
      "end_time": 147175.0,
      "text": "they tested whether it might be important for a vaccine"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 147199.0,
      "end_time": 149628.0,
      "text": "by conducting a cohort study."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 150307.0,
      "end_time": 155879.0,
      "text": "This typically involved about 300 participants in a village in Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 155903.0,
      "end_time": 158712.0,
      "text": "whose samples were analyzed to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 158736.0,
      "end_time": 164441.0,
      "text": "whether antibodies to the protein would predict who got malaria"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 164466.0,
      "end_time": 165712.0,
      "text": "and who did not."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 166323.0,
      "end_time": 168426.0,
      "text": "In the past 30 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 168450.0,
      "end_time": 173227.0,
      "text": "these studies have tested a small number of proteins"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 173252.0,
      "end_time": 175624.0,
      "text": "in relatively few samples"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 175648.0,
      "end_time": 178315.0,
      "text": "and usually in single locations."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 178782.0,
      "end_time": 181861.0,
      "text": "The results have not been consistent."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 182956.0,
      "end_time": 189360.0,
      "text": "My team essentially collapsed 30 years of this type of research"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 189610.0,
      "end_time": 194200.0,
      "text": "into one exciting experiment, conducted over just three months."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 194609.0,
      "end_time": 198831.0,
      "text": "Innovatively, we assembled 10,000 samples"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 198855.0,
      "end_time": 203268.0,
      "text": "from 15 locations in seven African countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 203292.0,
      "end_time": 207514.0,
      "text": "spanning time, age and the variable intensity"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 207538.0,
      "end_time": 210220.0,
      "text": "of malaria experienced in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 210585.0,
      "end_time": 216244.0,
      "text": "We used omics intelligence to prioritize our parasite proteins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 216268.0,
      "end_time": 218268.0,
      "text": "synthesize them in the lab"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 218292.0,
      "end_time": 223960.0,
      "text": "and in short, recreated the malaria parasite on a chip."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 223585.0,
      "end_time": 227520.0,
      "text": "We did this in Africa, and we&#39;re very proud of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 227379.0,
      "end_time": 233554.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 233578.0,
      "end_time": 236689.0,
      "text": "The chip is a small glass slide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 236713.0,
      "end_time": 239108.0,
      "text": "but it gives us incredible power."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 240700.0,
      "end_time": 246174.0,
      "text": "We simultaneously gathered data on over 100 antibody responses."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 246592.0,
      "end_time": 248192.0,
      "text": "What are we looking for?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 248679.0,
      "end_time": 253314.0,
      "text": "The recipe behind a successful antibody response,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 253338.0,
      "end_time": 257702.0,
      "text": "so that we can predict what might make a good malaria vaccine."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 258680.0,
      "end_time": 260553.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re also trying to figure out"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 260577.0,
      "end_time": 264124.0,
      "text": "exactly what antibodies do to the parasite."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 264482.0,
      "end_time": 266370.0,
      "text": "How do they kill it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 266610.0,
      "end_time": 269782.0,
      "text": "Do they attack from multiple angles? Is there synergy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 269807.0,
      "end_time": 271807.0,
      "text": "How much antibody do you need?"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 272188.0,
      "end_time": 278770.0,
      "text": "Our studies suggest that having a bit of one antibody won&#39;t be enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 278458.0,
      "end_time": 281641.0,
      "text": "It might take high concentrations of antibodies"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 281665.0,
      "end_time": 284181.0,
      "text": "against multiple parasite proteins."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 284673.0,
      "end_time": 289688.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re also learning that antibodies kill the parasite in multiple ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 289712.0,
      "end_time": 295656.0,
      "text": "and studying any one of these in isolation may not adequately reflect reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 296454.0,
      "end_time": 300930.0,
      "text": "Just like we can now see the parasite in greater definition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 300954.0,
      "end_time": 302946.0,
      "text": "my team and I are focused"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 302970.0,
      "end_time": 307707.0,
      "text": "on understanding how our bodies overcome this complexity."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 308120.0,
      "end_time": 312449.0,
      "text": "We believe that this could provide the breakthroughs that we need"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 312473.0,
      "end_time": 316209.0,
      "text": "to make malaria history through vaccination."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 316719.0,
      "end_time": 317870.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 317894.0,
      "end_time": 319597.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 319621.0,
      "end_time": 322170.0,
      "text": "(Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 322410.0,
      "end_time": 327793.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 327817.0,
      "end_time": 331304.0,
      "text": "Shoham Arad: OK, how close are we actually to a malaria vaccine?"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 332281.0,
      "end_time": 335138.0,
      "text": "Faith Osier: We&#39;re just at the beginning of a process"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 335162.0,
      "end_time": 339145.0,
      "text": "to try and understand what we need to put in the vaccine"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 339170.0,
      "end_time": 341703.0,
      "text": "before we actually start making it."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 341727.0,
      "end_time": 345560.0,
      "text": "So, we&#39;re not really close to the vaccine, but we&#39;re getting there."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 345584.0,
      "end_time": 346825.0,
      "text": "SA: And we&#39;re hopeful."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 346849.0,
      "end_time": 348649.0,
      "text": "FO: And we&#39;re very hopeful."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 349323.0,
      "end_time": 352568.0,
      "text": "SA: Tell me about SMART, tell me what does it stand for"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 352593.0,
      "end_time": 354633.0,
      "text": "and why is it important to you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 354657.0,
      "end_time": 361390.0,
      "text": "FO: So SMART stands for South-South Malaria Antigen Research Partnership."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 361477.0,
      "end_time": 365739.0,
      "text": "The South-South is referring to us in Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 365763.0,
      "end_time": 370268.0,
      "text": "looking sideways to each other in collaboration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 370292.0,
      "end_time": 374498.0,
      "text": "in contrast to always looking to America and looking to Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 374522.0,
      "end_time": 377558.0,
      "text": "when there is quite some strength within Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 377997.0,
      "end_time": 379161.0,
      "text": "So in SMART,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 379185.0,
      "end_time": 383125.0,
      "text": "apart from the goal that we have, to develop a malaria vaccine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 383149.0,
      "end_time": 385594.0,
      "text": "we are also training African scientists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 385618.0,
      "end_time": 388847.0,
      "text": "because the burden of disease in Africa is high,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 388871.0,
      "end_time": 392834.0,
      "text": "and you need people who will continue to push the boundaries"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 392858.0,
      "end_time": 394516.0,
      "text": "in science, in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 394540.0,
      "end_time": 396586.0,
      "text": "SA: Yes, yes, correct."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 396610.0,
      "end_time": 399801.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 400530.0,
      "end_time": 401601.0,
      "text": "OK, one last question."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 401625.0,
      "end_time": 404379.0,
      "text": "Tell me, I know you mentioned this a little bit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 404403.0,
      "end_time": 407657.0,
      "text": "but how would things actually change if there were a malaria vaccine?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 408732.0,
      "end_time": 412470.0,
      "text": "FO: We would save half a million lives every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 413256.0,
      "end_time": 415820.0,
      "text": "Two hundred million cases."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 415106.0,
      "end_time": 421914.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s estimated that malaria costs Africa 12 billion US dollars a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 422278.0,
      "end_time": 423674.0,
      "text": "So this is economics."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 423698.0,
      "end_time": 425965.0,
      "text": "Africa would simply thrive."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 426626.0,
      "end_time": 428126.0,
      "text": "SA: OK. Thank you, Faith."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 428151.0,
      "end_time": 429349.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 429373.0,
      "end_time": 430769.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}